This project is a frontend-only product prototype for a narrative consistency checking platform.

Follow docs/product_spec.md as the primary requirement source.
Use docs/reference.pdf as supporting reference only.

Important rules:
- Build a demo-ready web app prototype, not a real AI backend.
- Use mock data only.
- Prioritize UI completeness and product presentation.
- The product is not a generic business dashboard; it is an AI-assisted narrative consistency analysis console.
- Include pages for dashboard, upload/project management, conflict results, character consistency, knowledge graph view, and report export.
- Use Next.js + Tailwind CSS.
- Prefer reusable components and clean folder structure.
- Before coding, provide a concise implementation plan.